text: cng klaw theid (muhammad) wa thæcring sing thi phracea khxng chanth rng ham nan khux brrda sing thi chawcha na rangkeiyc thang pen sing thi peidphey cak man læa sing thi mi peidphey læa sing thi pen bap læa kar khmheng rangkæ doy mi pen thrrm læa kar thi phwk cea hı pen phakh kæ xallxh sung sing thi phraxngkh midi thrng prathan hlakthan dı «lng ma kæ sing nan læa kar thi phwk cea klaw hı phay kæ xallxh nı sing thi phwk cea miru
